        "id": "GvnEN18lnlck"
      },
      "source": [
        "### Singular Value Spectra By Layer\n",
        "- All layer show steep drop off from index 0 : The residual stream is low-rank meaning a few directions dominate in the small token sequence we gave.\n",
        "- Layer 0 has the lowest magnitude overall: Each layers havent accumulated much yet into the residual stream.\n",
        "- Later Layers (9,11) have higher singluar values : Attention + MLP writes have grown the nrom and spread it into the stream\n",
        "- The residual stream is not using unformly in all token dimensions some directions stay privilegded\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "### Variance Compression By Layer:\n",
        "- Layer 0 needs 8-9 components for 95% variance: Early residual stream is nearly rank-equal to the number of tokens - no strong compression.\n",
        "- Layers 3-11 reach 95% with just 2-3 components : MLP and attention progressively compress representations into fewer dominant directions.\n",
        "- Convergence gets faster in deeper layers: Deeper layers write into a more structured , lower-rank subspace informantion becomes more focused.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Effective Dimensionality by Layer:\n",
        "- Layer 0 needs 10 components: Tokens are independent at embedding\n",
        "- Layers 1-11 drop to ~1-3: One block is enought to collapse the stream to near rank-1\n",
        "- Far belwo d_model for shorter token sequence: Model uses only a tiny fraction of its capacity for short seqences in the respresentation space.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Variance by Top-K Components:\n",
        "top 1 jumps from 60-97 by layer 2 : A single direction quickly dominates the stream.\n",
        "top-10: 100% from layer 1 onward: Only 10 directions carry all meaningful token variation\n",
        "top - 100 : Botton singular dimensions are unused noise.\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "Core Claim:\n",
        "> Overall the residual stream of the transformer operates in a low-dimensional subspace for tokens of shorter sequence length , and this compression is well establised within first 1-2 layers mainted throughput"
      ]
    },
