      "source": [
        "# Logit Lens - Projecting Residual Stream to Vocabulary:\n",
        "\n",
        "## Experiment 1.4: Logit Lens Sanity Check\n",
        "\n",
        "The unembedding matrix $W_U \\in \\mathbb{R}^{d_{model} \\times |V|}$ projects\n",
        "residual stream vectors onto vocabulary space.\n",
        "\n",
        "The \"logit lens\" at layer $l$:\n",
        "$$\\text{logits}^{(l)} = x^{(l)} W_U$$\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "This asks: \"If we stopped at layer $l$ and immediately predicted the next token,\n",
        "how good would the prediction be?\"\n",
        "\n",
        "Hypothesis: Logit lens quality improves monotonically with depth.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 91,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "65dQMv5XtYqp"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "def compute_logit_lens(cache, model, n_layers, tokens_input, batch_idx=0):\n",
        "    true_next = tokens_input[0, 1:].cpu().numpy()\n",
        "\n",
        "    metrics = {\n",
        "        'top1_acc': [],\n",
        "        'entropy': [],\n",
        "        'true_token_rank': [],\n",
        "        'true_token_prob': []\n",
        "    }\n",
        "\n",
        "    for l in range(n_layers):\n",
        "        x = cache[f'blocks.{l}.hook_resid_post'][batch_idx]  # [T, d_model]\n",
        "\n",
        "        # TransformerLens correct way: apply_ln_to_stack handles ln_final + scaling\n",
        "        logits = model.unembed(model.ln_final(x)).detach().cpu().numpy()  # [T, d_vocab]\n",
        "\n",
        "        probs = torch.softmax(torch.tensor(logits[:-1]), dim=-1).numpy()\n",
        "\n",
        "        top1_preds = np.argmax(logits[:-1], axis=-1)\n",
        "        metrics['top1_acc'].append(np.mean(top1_preds == true_next))\n",
        "\n",
        "        ent = -np.sum(probs * np.log(probs + 1e-10), axis=-1).mean()\n",
        "        metrics['entropy'].append(ent)\n",
        "\n",
        "        ranks, true_probs = [], []\n",
        "        for pos in range(len(true_next)):\n",
        "            true_tok = true_next[pos]\n",
        "            sorted_indices = np.argsort(-logits[pos])\n",
        "            ranks.append(np.where(sorted_indices == true_tok)[0][0] + 1)\n",
        "            true_probs.append(probs[pos, true_tok])\n",
        "\n",
        "        metrics['true_token_rank'].append(np.mean(ranks))\n",
        "        metrics['true_token_prob'].append(np.mean(true_probs))\n",
        "\n",
        "    return metrics"
      ]
    },
