      "source": [
        "### The outlier L9H8:\n",
        "A rank ~10 ov circuit in an otherwise full-rank landscape means this head has learned a strongly compressed, low-rank write operation. It moves information along very few directions into the residual stream , (it can be a specialized function head)\n",
        "This is worth investigating"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "_GZ_nyA36oP3"
      }
    },
