    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### Attention Sink Head\n",
        "\n",
        "The pattern is very clear. Almost every token attends strongly to `<|endoftext|>` (The BOS token) is an attention sink head, not a name mover head.\n",
        "\n",
        "The rank-10 OV isnt because this head is doing something strong and sophisticated , its because its mostly dead. An attention sink head that always attends to BOS only needds to write one thing, hence near rank-1 behavior in practice despite the rank-10 by the 95% threshold."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "hpS5UWkg8Ajn"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "attention_patterns = []\n",
        "for l in range(model.cfg.n_layers):\n",
        "    attn = cache[f'blocks.{l}.attn.hook_pattern'][0]  # [n_heads, n_tokens, n_tokens]\n",
        "    attention_patterns.append(attn.cpu().numpy())\n",
        "\n",
        "# Use CircuitsVis for interactive attention visualization\n",
        "# This will render in the notebook\n",
        "token_strings = model.to_str_tokens(prompt)"
      ],
